data.description: Beautiful updated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage home. This home features newer stainless appliances, hood fan, farm style sink, floating shelves, tons of cabinets and LVT flooring in kitchen and dining room. Sun filled foyer, sunroom and living room with oak flooring. The upper level has 3 bedrooms and a full bathroom with tile flooring and slate surround.  Plenty of storage space in the upper level as well. Lower level was refinished and includes a gas fireplace with slate surround when sellers moved in. This space is so versatile. It could be a family room, owner's suite or guest space.  Walk out to 1 of your 2 large decks.  Newer water heater. Roof 6 years old. Fabulous outdoor space, decks, patios, fenced yard and more!!
